name: Thai Elephant OR Bedroom Window
description:
Best Sellers

Choose between:
Thai Elephant: A film image taken in Bangkok, Thailand, in November of 2011.
OR
Bedroom Windown: A film image taken at La Guillone B&B in Gordes, France, in May of 2011.

Camera information: Contax 645 with Planar T* 80mm f2 lens

Please leave a message through Paypal [there is an option to add a "note to seller" on the "Review your Information" page] or send a message through the "contact" button at the right with your print choice(s). Thank you!

Processed, scanned, and printed on Fuji Matte photographic paper by Richard Photo Lab.

Images will be sized on the print with a one-inch border for 8x10", a two-inch border for 12x16", and a three-inch border for 16x20".

8x10" fits the $10 IKEA Ribba frame. 
12x16" fits the $15 IKEA Ribba frame. 
16x20" fits the $20 IKEA Ribba frame.
